2.scbdd.com/server/interact/38/', '[1] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Yondelis (trabectedin)." Janssen Pharmaceuticals, Titusville, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Velpatasvir, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, Brincidofovir, More', 'Vincristine, Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Paclitaxel, Topotecan, Teniposide, Irinotecan, Vinorelbine, Etoposide, Docetaxel', 1767369485);
